<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>상품관리 | DAMORE ADMIN</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f3ef;
      --white: #fff;
      --black: #111;
      --muted: #6f6a63;
      --line: rgba(17,17,17,0.08);
      --gold: #9d8660;
      --green: #1f7a45;
      --green-bg: #edf7f0;
      --red: #b23a2c;
      --red-bg: #fff1ee;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --max: 1320px;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Pretendard","Noto Sans KR",Arial,sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--black);
    }

    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
    button { font: inherit; }

    .container {
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .topbar {
      background: var(--black);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 40px 0 80px;
    }

    .head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 20px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .head small {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .head h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .head p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .head-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .create-btn {
      min-width: 180px;
      height: 52px;
      padding: 0 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--black);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .dashboard-btn {
      min-width: 180px;
      height: 52px;
      padding: 0 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #efe9df;
      color: var(--black);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr auto;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .thumb {
      width: 140px;
      height: 170px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #f0ede8;
    }

    .thumb img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .thumb-empty {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .meta {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .badges {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 34px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .badge-active {
      background: var(--green-bg);
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .badge-soldout {
      background: var(--red-bg);
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .badge-best {
      background: #efe9df;
      color: #6a5943;
    }

    .stock-box {
      margin-top: 12px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .stock-box strong {
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .action-col {
      width: 200px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 44px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 0 14px;
    }

    .btn-dark {
      background: var(--black);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-light {
      background: #efe9df;
      color: var(--black);
    }

    .btn-red {
      background: var(--red-bg);
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .empty {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 40px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .empty h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .empty p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .thumb {
        width: 100%;
        height: 260px;
      }

      .action-col {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .container { padding: 0 16px; }
      .create-btn,
      .dashboard-btn { width: 100%; }
      .head-actions { width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">DAMORE ADMIN PANEL</div>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="head">
        <div>
          <small>Product Management</small>
          <h1>상품관리</h1>
          <p>재고 수량과 자동 품절 상태를 함께 관리하는 버전입니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="head-actions">
          <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="dashboard-btn">관리자 대시보드</a>
          <a href="/admin/products/new" class="create-btn">새 상품 등록</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <% if (!products || products.length === 0) { %>
        <div class="empty">
          <h2>등록된 상품이 없습니다.</h2>
          <p>먼저 상품을 등록해보세요.</p>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <div class="grid">
          <% products.forEach(product => { %>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="thumb">
                  <% if (product.image) { %>
                    <img src="<%= product.image %>" alt="<%= product.name %>" />
                  <% } else { %>
                    <div class="thumb-empty">이미지 없음</div>
                  <% } %>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <div class="title"><%= product.name %></div>

                  <div class="meta">
                    카테고리: <%= product.category || '-' %><br />
                    판매가: <%= Number(product.price || 0).toLocaleString() %>원<br />
                    기존가: <%= Number(product.oldPrice || 0).toLocaleString() %>원<br />
                    옵션: <%= product.options && product.options.length ? product.options.join(', ') : '없음' %>
                  </div>

                  <div class="badges">
                    <% if ((product.stock || 0) > 0) { %>
                      <span class="badge badge-active">판매중</span>
                    <% } else { %>
                      <span class="badge badge-soldout">품절</span>
                    <% } %>

                    <% if (product.isBest) { %>
                      <span class="badge badge-best">BEST</span>
                    <% } %>
                  </div>

                  <div class="stock-box">
                    현재 재고:
                    <strong><%= Number(product.stock || 0).toLocaleString() %>개</strong>
                    <% if ((product.stock || 0) <= 0) { %>
                      / 자동 품절 상태
                    <% } %>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="action-col">
                  <a href="/admin/products/<%= product._id %>/edit" class="btn btn-dark">상품 수정</a>

                  <form method="POST" action="/admin/products/<%= product._id %>/best">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light">
                      <%= product.isBest ? 'BEST 해제' : 'BEST 지정' %>
                    </button>
                  </form>

                  <form
                    method="POST"
                    action="/admin/products/<%= product._id %>/delete"
                    onsubmit="return confirm('정말 이 상품을 삭제할까요?');"
                  >
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-red">상품 삭제</button>
                  </form>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>